com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface Feature

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Document, Folder, PlaceMark

    public interface Feature
    This interface represents the abstract <Feature> tag from KML specification.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • SIMPLE_DATA

        static final java.lang.String SIMPLE_DATA
        This constant defines a simple data element within the extended data structure. These are name values pairs where the name is an attribute of the element and the value is the text of the element. 

        
 <ExtendedData>
        
   <SimpleData name="foo">Bar</SimpleData>
        
   <SimpleData name="foo2">Bar2</SimpleData>
        
 </ExtendedData>

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • DATA

        static final java.lang.String DATA
        This constant defines a data element within the extended data structure. These are embedded value elements within a data element. 

        
 <ExtendedData>
        
   <Data name="foo">
        
     <value>Bar</value>
        
   </Data>
        
   <Data name="foo2">
        
     <value>Bar2</value>
        
   </Data>
        
 </ExtendedData>

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
